  "detailed_description": "The Magnets is a logic puzzle game whose goal is to make the balls fall onto the same colored platforms by using the magnets to push or pull the blocks.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The magnets <strong>push</strong> the blocks of the <strong>same color</strong> and <strong>pull</strong> the <strong>different colored blocks</strong>, <strong>only if the number</strong> on the magnets is <strong>greater</strong> than the number on the block.<br></li><li> <strong>The numbers</strong> on the magnet show their <strong>strength against the blocks</strong>, and also how many squares their <strong>field of view</strong> and <strong> impact area</strong> are.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532780/extras/b52e420dc3ebd86ffad8f82345eb601a.poster.avif?t=1628347214\" width=600 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532780/extras/b52e420dc3ebd86ffad8f82345eb601a.webm?t=1628347214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No time and life limitation<br></li><li> Difficulty increases steadily along the course of the game<br></li><li> You can undo your move or restart the level whenever you want<br></li><li> You can quit from a puzzle whenever you want, then you can come back and continue where you left off</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532780/extras/1a9be5c64339af7c0c8fa2919cd8353e.avif?t=1628347214\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
